1) Compile the Java code into a JAR file. Make sure to also include all necessary dependencies for Bukkit/Spigot.
2) Place the JAR file on your Bukkit/Spigot server in the plugins folder.
3) Start or restart the Minecraft server.
4) Log into the game as an administrator.
5) Use the /setspawn command in the game to set the spawn point to your current location.
